                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9476" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1429</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1583 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">混改背景下舍得酒业两次控制权安排的“舍”与“得”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The &quot;lose&quot; and &quot;gains&quot; of the two control rights arrangement of Shede Spirits under the background of mixed reform</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杨海燕，简华君</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广西大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">舍得酒业股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国企混改；控制权安排；公司治理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">mixed ownership reform, control rights arrangement, corporate governance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国有企业混合所有制改革中引入民营股东有利于解决国企“所有者缺位”的问题，可以完善公司治理，促进国企进行市场化改革。然而当民营股东控股且缺乏制衡时，其掏空动机可能大于监督动机从而导致机会主义行为，带来治理风险。权力过于集中且缺乏制衡就容易产生第一类代理问题，若权力分散就容易产生“内部人控制”问题。因此，良好的公司治理需要依赖于合理的控制权安排。控制权安排是财务管理、公司治理教学的重要内容之一。本案例描述了舍得酒业两次混改的过程以及混改后公司的发展状况，让学生系统的了解控制权安排的变化对企业发展的影响；全面掌握国企混改以及控制权安排的含义、作用、条件、动机和经济后果；深入思考化解国企混改中的控制权风险的方法。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The introduction of private shareholders in the mixed ownership reform of state-owned enterprises is conducive to solving the problem of &quot;owner vacancy&quot; in state-owned enterprises. Private shareholders will improve corporate governance based on the motivation of &quot;supervision&quot; and promote market-oriented reform of state-owned enterprises. However, when private shareholders hold controlling shares and lack checks and balances, their tunneling motivation may be greater than their supervisory motivation, leading to opportunistic behavior and governance risks. Excessive concentration of power and lack of checks and balances can easily lead to the first type of agency problem, while if power is dispersed, it can easily lead to &quot;insider control&quot; problems. So good corporate governance requires a reasonable arrangement of control rights. Control arrangement is one of the important contents of financial management and corporate governance education. This case describes the process of two mixed ownership reforms in Shede Liquor Industry and the development status of the company after the mixed ownership reform, allowing students to systematically understand the impact of changes in control arrangements on the development of the enterprise; Fully grasp the meaning, role, conditions, motivations, and economic consequences of mixed ownership reform of state-owned enterprises and control arrangements; Deeply consider methods to mitigate control risks in the mixed ownership reform of state-owned enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理》、《公司理财》、《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国企混改的含义、动机、经济后果；控制权安排的含义、经济后果；产权理论；超产权理论；委托代理理论；协同效应理论；公司治理理论。</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
